  - Data Agent used MCP tools

Final answer:
 {
  "type": "get_customer",
  "customer_id": 5,
  "customer": {
    "customer": {
      "id": 5,
      "name": "Charlie Brown",
      "email": "charlie.brown@email.com",
      "phone": "+1-555-0105",
      "status": "active",
      "created_at": "2025-12-01 19:53:51",
      "updated_at": "2025-12-01 19:53:51"
