TEST: Escalation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Query: I've been charged twice, please refund immediately!

Scenario: support
Route: router -> support
Logs:
  - Router classified as SUPPORT

Final answer:
 I understand your concern regarding the double charge, and I apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused. To assist you further, please provide the transaction details (date and amounts) so we can expedite the refund process.

